Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:07.79,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}優しく食むわ　あなたの全てを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:12.99,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur3\fad(150,150)}It's my guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:26.34,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}気づく　目を見開いてる
