Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:28.82,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}这暗蓝色的混凝土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:31.30,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}冰冷地将我包裹
Comment: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:33.76,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Call my name and give me a kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:36.28,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}而后将我揽入胸怀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.28,0:21:42.82,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}用你那已经失去灵魂的躯体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:45.62,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}濒临崩溃的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.62,0:21:52.97,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}仍勉强维持姿态
