Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.59,0:21:59.67,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}它就在我身旁放声歌唱
Comment: 0,0:21:59.82,0:22:02.79,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}What was I born for
